{"tid":2183700,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber司機被裁定非法載客取酬罪成　提終極上訴被裁敗訴","createTime":"2020-09-01T05:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T09:52:54.000Z","uid":88592,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e966e3255517f7f028212e61dc75c0c2efb8a8e9","tid":2183700,"uid":88592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"警方於2017年扮乘客「放蛇」，拘捕多名Uber司機。28名司機事後遭裁定駕駛汽車非法載客取酬罪罪成，被判罰款。而其中24名司機向高等法院提出上訴，但去年遭駁回，他們再向終審法院提出終極上訴。終院5名法官今（1日）聽取陳詞後，即駁回上訴，稍後以書面頒下判辭解釋詳細理據。<br />\n是次上訴涉及24名司機，上訴人要求院就《道路交通條例》第52（3）條，釐清有關「以作出租或取酬載客用途」的控罪元素的恰當詮釋。其代表律師今陳詞時指，認為相關法例需證明司機和乘客之間有直接協議。惟Uber司機接載乘客，是基於Uber的安排，而非司機和乘客之間的協議。惟法官聽取陳辭後即駁回其申請。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FACC 1/2020<br />\n<br />\nSource:hk01 廢事貼link"},{"pid":"9765aeb2b61786c75be368ca0d9df111ee89e40f","tid":2183700,"uid":119607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"黨媒truth hk又出fake news 又用721微博假圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2183510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2183510</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1bb321d0e229d2f6e31283dab4fbe6512d66fb9c","tid":2183700,"uid":9230,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"一句到尾，個客唔俾錢你會唔會車佢嗰程車？<br />\n<br />\n但我同意將Uber 合法化，起碼要啲車買商業車保險，要啲司機拎6號牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0ab9502f6df579f95ab373cafce426ce4d5500","tid":2183700,"uid":1748,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"Uber將錢嘅單位轉成分計會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個客要用服務就用錢入分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe547d245c52526bbfb6f794e4b83b2ba8af2fe","tid":2183700,"uid":9230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fe0ab9502f6df579f95ab373cafce426ce4d5500","tid":2183700,"uid":1748,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"Uber將錢嘅單位轉成分計會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個客要用服務就用錢入分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"你試吓用分賣白粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本「報酬」嘅媒介同去點由個客轉到去司機都唔係重點，而係個司機係唔係因為有利益去驅使佢去車陌生人"},{"pid":"5104cf93c7f6881b05cfaf987d8a7a67a08e76ad","tid":2183700,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8674ac76fdc5eae6b4b253e400cd88cda731a50","tid":2183700,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbe547d245c52526bbfb6f794e4b83b2ba8af2fe","tid":2183700,"uid":9230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fe0ab9502f6df579f95ab373cafce426ce4d5500","tid":2183700,"uid":1748,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"Uber將錢嘅單位轉成分計會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個客要用服務就用錢入分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"你試吓用分賣白粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本「報酬」嘅媒介同去點由個客轉到去司機都唔係重點，而係個司機係唔係因為有利益去驅使佢去車陌生人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:51:57.000Z","msg":"所以如果用car pooling 去比較就有可拗性<br />\n<br />\n一個人願意車一班順路嘅人。乘客自願分攤一啲清析嘅開支（如隧道費）。喺現行法例仍然可以告載客取酬，但就真心唔合理喇。因為司機無意圖去「營業」，佢就算無客，該旅程仍然會發生"},{"pid":"bb715ad7846d05764f99bf908fb560e71a3fd533","tid":2183700,"uid":25727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fe0ab9502f6df579f95ab373cafce426ce4d5500","tid":2183700,"uid":1748,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:29:27.000Z","msg":"Uber將錢嘅單位轉成分計會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個客要用服務就用錢入分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"有心搞你咪好似掃黃咁 捉你周邊罪行 諸如非法改裝 扣留你架車等你開唔到工<br />\n再